      <h3 class="collection-teaser__title"><a href="/our-work/research-reports/legislative-assaults-state-courts-may-2021-update">Legislative Assaults on State Courts — May 2021 Update</a></h3>
      <div class="collection-teaser__description"><p>State lawmakers across the country are considering bills that would diminish the role or independence of state courts. And some bills appear to be targeting courts for their role in election-related cases.</p></div>
