              <div class="teaser__tophat">Analysis</div>
            <h3 class="teaser__title"><a href="/our-work/analysis-opinion/poll-election-officials-finds-concerns-about-safety-political"><p>Poll of Election Officials Finds Concerns About Safety, Political Interference</p></a></h3>
      <div class="teaser__description"><p>The vast majority of local election officials have taken new precautions to secure the 2024 election.</p></div>

              <div class="teaser__meta">
                      <div class="teaser__authors">
                              <span class="author--inline">
            <span><a href="/about/staff/ruby-edlin" hreflang="en">Ruby Edlin</a></span>
      
, </span>
                              <span class="author--inline">
            <span><a href="/about/leadership/lawrence-norden" hreflang="en">Lawrence Norden</a></span>
      
</span>
                          </div>
                                <div class="teaser__date with-separator">May 1, 2024</div>
                  </div>
      
    </div>

  </article>
</li>



<li class="teaser-list__list-item">
